  "body": "Hello Truffle team,\r\n\r\nNot sure who to contact, but if it can help the community, here is a step by step github [guide](https://github.com/gregbkr/geth-truffle-docker) and [blog](https://greg.satoshi.tech/deploy-your-first-smart-contract-with-this-base-ethereum-truffle-setup/) on how to use Geth+Truffle in docker, and how to deploy and interact with few easy smart contracts (greeter, metacoin, counter). \r\n\r\nI am maintaining it for the Geneva Dev [meetup](https://www.meetup.com/Geneva-DevChain-UserGroup/) team, where we on-board new comers every months. \r\n\r\nFeel free to close this issue.\r\n\r\nThank you for any feedback and very good week!\r\nKeep up the good/awesome work! \r\nGreg.",
